Package gw.api.rest.framework.v1

Class PageInfo

java.lang.Object
gw.api.rest.framework.v1.PageInfo
public class PageInfo extends Object
This class has information about the page, both configuration like page size and limits; execution like total count and count; and presentation like names for items, count, totalCount and links.

    • PageInfo

      public PageInfo()
      Default constructor for tests

    • PageInfo

      public PageInfo(RequestContext context)
      Constructor which will extract the configuration information from the request parameters. It will also retain the context so that the page links can be created.
      Parameters:
      context - the request context

    • PageInfo

      public PageInfo(int start, int pageSize, int fetchLimit, boolean totalCountDesired, RequestContext requestContext)
      Constructor which will permit the called to define the page configuration information directly. It will also retain the context so that the page links can be created.
      Parameters:
      start - the index to start at default is zero
      pageSize - the number or items to include in this page, page size of zero will just report the total count
      fetchLimit - the maximum number of rows to process
      totalCountDesired - whether to include the total number of items (upto the limit) that could be reported
      requestContext - the request context
